Description: Print Automation Server
 Central server for coordinating print jobs across multiple
 Windows client machines. Provides REST API, web dashboard,
 and automatic load balancing for Konica Minolta production
 printers.
 .
 Features:
  - Token-based client authentication
  - Intelligent job routing to least-loaded printer
  - Excel receipt generation with Celery + openpyxl
  - Real-time web dashboard with printer status
  - PostgreSQL persistence with async SQLAlchemy
  - Redis-backed Celery task queue
  - SSL termination via Nginx reverse proxy
